up|BT]] Digital Awards: Breakthrough Artist of the Year||{{won}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nme.com/news/muse/31529|title=Muse win BT Digital Music Award|website=Nmre.com|date=3 October 2007}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|2009|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Kerrang! Awards#2009 Results|Kerrang! Awards 2009]]: Best Live Band||{{nom}}<ref name=\"blog.kerrangawards.com\">{{cite web |url=http://blog.kerrangawards.com/2009/2009/08/best_british_band.shtml |title=Archived copy |accessdate=23 February 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100227043629/http://blog.kerrangawards.com/2009/2009/08/best_british_band.shtml |archivedate=27 February 2010  }}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|2010|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Kerrang! Awards 2010]]: Best British Band||{{nom}}<ref name=\"blog.kerrangawards.com\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"6\"|2012|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Kerrang! Awards 2012]]: Best Live Band||{{won}}<ref name=\"kerrang2012\">{{cite news |title=And the nominees are... |work=[[Kerrang!]] |publisher=[[Bauer Media Group]] |url=http://www.kerrang.com/blog/2012/05/and_the_nominees_are_2.html |date=2 May 2012 |accessdate=2 May 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510023850/http://www.kerrang.com/blog/2012/05/and_the_nominees_are_2.html |archivedate=10 May 2012  }}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|''[[A Flash Flood of Colour]]''|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Kerrang! Awards 2012]]: Best Album||{{nom}}<ref name=\"kerrang2012\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|Rou Reynolds|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Kerrang! Awards 2012]]: Hero of the Year||{{won}}<ref name=\"kerrang2012\"/>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"2\"|Enter Shikari|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Association of Independent Music|AIM]] Awards: Hardest Working Band||{{nom}}<ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web|url=http://www.musicindie.com/awards/winners2012|title=Winners 20