om/heavy-music-awards-2017-winners-announced |title=Heavy Music Awards 2017 Winners |publisher=Heavy Music Awards |author=Heavy Music Awards |date=24 August 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|2018||style=\"text-align:center;\"|''[[The Spark (Enter Shikari album)|The Spark]]''|| style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[Kerrang! Awards 2018]]: Best Album||{{won}}\n|}\n;Miscellaneous\n* [[Rock Sound]]'s poll for 'who will make it in 2007'.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rock-sound.net/view_news.php?headline%3DENTER-SHIKARI-WIN%26id%3D2004102713 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=13 June 2007 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071013183110/http://rock-sound.net/view_news.php?headline=ENTER-SHIKARI-WIN&id=2004102713 |archivedate=13 October 2007  }}</ref>\n* Ourzone Reader's Poll: Best Live Band 2011.<ref name=\"By Richard on 3 December 2011\">{{cite web |author=Richard on |url=http://ourzonemag.com/oz/2011-ourzone-readers-poll-results |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120530073451/http://ourzonemag.com/oz/2011-ourzone-readers-poll-results |url-status=dead |archive-date=30 May 2012 |title=2011 Ourzone Readers Poll results &#124; Ourzone Magazine |publisher=Ourzonemag.com |date=3 December 2011 |accessdate=4 February 2012 }}</ref>\n* Ourzone Reader's Poll: Who Will Own 2012.<ref name=\"By Richard on 3 December 2011\"/>\n* [[NME]]'s User's Poll: Best Act at [[Reading and Leeds Festivals]] 2012.<ref name=\"By Mythophonic on 5 September 2012\">{{cite web|author=|url=https://www.nme.com/news/enter-shikari/65835 |title=NME Best Act At Reading And Leeds 2012 |website=Nme.com|date=5 September 2012 |accessdate=5 September 2012}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Official website|http://www.entershikari.com}}\n\n{{Enter Shikari}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Enter Shikari|*]]\n[[Category:British post-hardcore musical groups]]\n[[Category:Electronicore musical groups]]\n[[Category:English alternative rock 